    "The system's value diminishes significantly if the cases presented to developers are frequently incorrect or unhelpful.",
    "Efficient technologies for accumulating cases, such as automatic analysis of software repositories, are necessary.",
    "The type of cases needed also varies depending on whether the developer needs ideas for the upstream process or is struggling with the downstream process.",
    "Therefore, constructing a system that can provide appropriate cases tailored to the purpose is essential.",
    "Finally, the most significant limitation and a key theme for future research is that the actual development and provision of the services intended by the users have not been carried out."
